Coy Watson Jr. https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Coy_Watson_Jr. 0 James Caughey Watson Jr. (November 16, 1912 – March 14, 2009) professionally Coy Watson, was an American child actor of the silent era, who was from an extended family of fellow performers known as The Watson Family, he appeared in more than 60 films.
